Class GroupModel

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.im.njams.sdk.model.ActivityModel
      • com.im.njams.sdk.model.GroupModel

  • public class GroupModel
extends ActivityModel
    GroupModel is a Activity which represents a Group ind the ProcessModel. A Group can have child Activities.
